Package: ghostwriteR
Type: Package
Title: Translate R and SQL Workflows into Diagrams and Handoff Documents
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: c(
    person("crg0195", "maintainer", email = "crg0195@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Parses a single R script or SQL script and turns the workflow
    into a visual dependency map plus plain-language handoff materials.
    The package can produce graph objects, self-contained HTML pages,
    exportable diagrams, and written workflow summaries designed to help
    technical and non-technical collaborators understand how inputs,
    transformations, and outputs connect.
URL: https://github.com/crg0195/ghostwriteR
BugReports: https://github.com/crg0195/ghostwriteR/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
